"The '''Quantum Energy Generator''' (QEG) is a crisp, clean, and modern device based on Nikola Tesla’s public domain design".

In March 2014 the fabrication manual of the QEG was published as Open Source.

The PESWiki (Pure Energy Systems) qualifies the project as one of the ''five of the best exotic technologies we've found so far, which are closest to the market''.

